Package: berryFunctions
Type: Package
Title: Function Collection related to Hydrology, Zooming and Plotting
Version: 1.6.2
Date: 2014-10-27
Author: Berry Boessenkool
Maintainer: Berry Boessenkool <berry-b@gmx.de>
Description: collection of functions to: zoom in X11 graphics, use the unit hydrograph in a linear storage cascade, enhance log-axis plots, draw horizontal histograms and scatterplots colored by 3rd dimension, convert lists to data.frames, fit multiple functions (power, reciprocal, exponential, logarithmic, polynomial, rational) by regression. Development version: https://github.com/BerryBoessenkool
Suggests: RColorBrewer
License: GPL-2
